column5: OFC has a New Fishing TV Personality starting a new show. I won't say who it is.   I'll let him fill in the details and the name of the show. I know that I will be watching it for the great fishing and for the laughs as well.  Congratts Mr!!!! Great Job for sure!!!
GCD finally got his new show.  Can't wait to see "Coon Hounds and Crappie" - Homestyle Fishin with your host Green Coach Dawg.....
Yeah well he certainly deserves it!  Congrats to you "J".  Looking forward to that one for sure!
Roy...your "J" has her own fishing show?...I'm going to have to brush up on my French for sure now !
